question: Where can I find restaurant in the direction of Zagray Farm Museum, Colchester, CT within 140 kilometers from Miley Hall, RI?
sql:
WITH
    angle AS (SELECT degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-71.300803 41.474893)',4326)::geography, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-72.341878 41.597642)',4326)::geography)) AS value)
SELECT * FROM pois,angle
WHERE amenity = 'restaurant'
AND ST_DWithin(pois.geometry, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-71.300803 41.474893)',4326)::geography, 140000)
AND (degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-71.300803 41.474893)',4326)::geography, pois.geometry)) BETWEEN angle.value - 22.5 AND angle.value + 22.5);
